:4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:19:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a64e6c6797dc04d1c0d4b317b702d564ee0c9db1","tid":409952,"uid":61748,"like":88,"dislike":13,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f21903aa106f7ff0c018389f9be735f8d1fbb1e","tid":409952,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":37,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺人犯死左佢算啦<br />\n你點變好都係殺人犯黎架啦仆街</blockquote><br />\n反對"},{"pid":"a401ca22fa27f2c18e2c39f981984cc3e56d5076","tid":409952,"uid":111253,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>殺人犯死左佢算啦<br />\n你點變好都係殺人犯黎架啦仆街</blockquote><br />\n可能佢都死果條MK都係社會垃圾"},{"pid":"fbb1944000d11147024b40c752bfc614b1f5df34","tid":409952,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>殺人犯死左佢算啦<br />\n你點變好都係殺人犯黎架啦仆街</blockquote><br />\n可能佢斬死果條MK都係社會垃圾</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d12754e976bb201500fc31ce4fb1e25c07968138","tid":409952,"uid":98386,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"坐監啲人十個有七個都信耶穌 明明入去前就唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有唔該啲肥矮柒毒睇清楚人地講乜 咪左一句黑社會右一句黑社會大尻人 監獄就係你地既未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784d6bdb22a8de5695aa00418faf3feb1c76257d","tid":409952,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:30:56.000Z","msg":"死刑唔係1966年已停止執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382ab0d79ca8808e2070a5ce8766f146bc403e8b","tid":409952,"uid":130105,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死刑唔係1966年已停止執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係咁，個時照判，但就英皇一定會赦免，改為終身監禁，唔知佢知唔知；即係五餅二魚咁，你可以聽完就信，但也有個常理解釋。"},{"pid":"3678d1eea22048dfd45b5389262d681ce46eb